
the way to simulate loop keys(e.g. 123):
 . make a list init with keys+reverse keys - e.g. 123321
 . shift one then push it back - after one step 233211

the way to encrypt
 . make a list (a..za..z)
 . the encrypted character's index is ord($plaintext) - ord ('a') + $key

 the way to decrypt
 . make a list (z..az..a)
 . the decrypted character's index is ord('z') - ord( $cryptedtext) + $key

 
